OL,3,CPrincess Anne to open Jersey Zoo's new
OL,4,Cgorilla enclosure
OL,6,FJersey Zoo's long-awaited new gorilla
OL,7,Fhouse will be opened by the Princess
OL,8,FRoyal next month.
OL,10,FHer Royal Highness is a patron of the
OL,11,FDurrell Wildlife Conservation Trust,
OL,12,Fwhich runs the zoo, and will visit the
OL,13,Fisland on Thursday 30 April for the
OL,14,Fofficial unveiling.
OL,16,FThe multi-million-pound project
OL,17,Freplaces the current enclosure, which
OL,18,Fwas built more than 40 years ago.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
