CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1774368667
OL,3,CPrincess Anne to open Jersey Zoo's new
OL,4,Cgorilla enclosure
OL,6,FThe zoo currently looks after four
OL,7,Fcritically endangered westland lowland
OL,8,Fgorillas - called Badongo, Bahasha,
OL,9,FHlala Kahilli and Amari.
OL,11,FDurrell says the new gorilla house
OL,12,Fwill give them "much more space to
OL,13,Froam around in and be more
OL,14,Fsustainable".
OL,16,FIt will include a modern heating and
OL,17,Fcooling system, eight bedrooms, two
OL,18,Flarge indoor housing spaces and a
OL,19,Fseparate area for training and
OL,20,Fweighing the troop.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
