PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1774368667
OL,3,CPrincess Anne to open Jersey Zoo's new
OL,4,Cgorilla enclosure
OL,6,FIn 2019, 40 gorilla sculptures went
OL,7,Funder the hammer to raise money for
OL,8,Fthe project after being on public
OL,9,Fdisplay across Jersey, raising more
OL,10,Fthan #1.1 million.
OL,12,FThe development is the largest capital
OL,13,Fproject the zoo has carried out, with
OL,14,Fresearch balconies and full CCTV to
OL,15,Fmonitor the apes' behaviour.
OL,17,FIt was delayed by rising material
OL,18,Fcosts but is now nearly ready to open,
OL,19,Fwith a predicted cost of between #4
OL,20,Fmillion and #5 million.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/4
